Package: rtfreporter
Type: Package
Title: Clinical RTF Reporting Toolkit for Tables, Listings and Figures
Version: 0.3.13
Authors@R:
    person(given  = "Yoichi",
           family = "Masui",
           email  = "ichi.r.pro@gmail.com",
           role   = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: A standalone toolkit for generating Rich Text Format (RTF)
    reports used in clinical trial deliverables -- Tables, Listings and
    Figures (TFLs). Provides a functional, pipe-friendly API to compose
    documents with multi-section headers and footers, multi-row column
    headers including spanning groups, per-column formatting, automatic
    page-number fields, embedded PNG/JPEG figures, and clinical-style
    borders. Uses only S3 classes and base R; depends on no other
    RTF-generation packages such as 'r2rtf' or 'reporter'.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
